notesStmt.note: This workshop discussion focuses on the European youth pact and the employment situation of young people in Europe. The participants are representatives of different European youth organizations. They first discuss the results of a panel discussion that took place prior to this speech event in the context of the larger conference that this speech event is part of. The participants also report on their personal experiences in their individual countries and agree on how to proceed. S1 chairs the event and takes notes on the blackboard. S9 is responsible for the minutes and will present the outcome of the workshop discussion to a larger audience afterwards.

equipment.p: Portable minidisc recorder with electret condenser stereo microphone
